      "id": "PopularPost69762",
      "post_content": "You're right, flavorfully, this should be blue's. Wizards seems pretty dead set against giving this ability to blue, though. If blue wants to shut down combat, it taps things instead, such as in [Sleep](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sleep). Green still gets Fog, but [Darkness](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darkness) is pretty much gone. ",
      "posted_by": "ScissorsLizard",
