      "id": "PopularPost94765",
      "post_content": "Green gets a lot of things that seem \"in flavor\" for blue. Though blue has a domain over the sky's creatures, green has always had domain over the air as well- seen in the [squall](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=squall)s, [windstorm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=windstorm)s and [hurricane](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=hurricane)s on so many green cards.  \nI guess \"fog\" fits into the \"nature\" niche, which is very green.",
      "posted_by": "Kryptnyt",
